This will test that the MAAS server offers an option to periodically update cloud images.
<dl>
    <dt>Open the main page to the MAAS server</dt>
    <dt>Find the option in the MAAS server preferences to periodically update cloud images.</dt>
    <dt>Set it to automatically update</dt>
        <dd>Did you find the option to periodically update cloud images?</dd>
        <dd>Were the cloud images updated according to the schedule?</dd>
</dl>

This will test that the MAAS server offers an option to cache archives locally.
<dl>
    <dt>Open the main page to the MAAS server</dt>
    <dt>Find the option in the MAAS server preferences to cache archives locally</dt>
    <dt>Enable the option</dt>
        <dd>Did you find the option to cache archives locally?</dd>
        <dd>Verify archives are cached locally and nodes are using it to receive updates.</dd>
</dl>
